2
Related to racial composition (used in older studies)
Not commonly used today due to ethical concerns

LSTAT (Low Status Population)

👉 % of lower-income population

High LSTAT → poorer area → lower house prices
Low LSTAT → wealthy area → higher prices

LSTAT (Low Status Population)

👉 % of lower-income population

High LSTAT → poorer area → lower house prices
Low LSTAT → wealthy area → higher prices